  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith's sister leaves the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that Mrs. Dulangali Jayakodi, the sister of opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa, left the island yesterday (26) morning.",
        "It is reported that she has left the island with her two children, Sanjay Jayakodi and Amaya Jayakodi, on Sri Lankan Airlines flight UL 505 for London, England.",
        "Ms. Dulangali Jayakodi was summoned to the Criminal Investigation Department and recorded a statement on the last 20th regarding the incident of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe's personal house in Kollupitiya being destroyed by fire."
      ],
